## How to Run
I've added helper scripts to the root [package.json](file:///d:/kavi/portfolio/package.json):

- **Install All Dependencies**: `npm run install:all`
- **Start Both Client & Server**: `npm run start:all` (requires `concurrently`)
- **Start Backend Only**: `npm run start:server`
- **Start Frontend Only**: `npm run start:client`

